WEBVTT

00:00:01.000 --> 00:00:08.603
Forking a Repository

00:00:08.603 --> 00:00:19.248
One parent, many independent clones

00:00:19.248 --> 00:00:28.941
Sharing a link, not the folder

00:00:28.941 --> 00:00:40.236
Same speed at any size

00:00:40.236 --> 00:01:02.221
Step 1: Fork the repo

00:01:02.221 --> 00:01:20.298
Step 2: Both repos side by side

00:01:20.298 --> 00:01:37.947
Step 3: Original is untouched

00:01:37.947 --> 00:01:49.312
The sun and the mirror

00:01:49.312 --> 00:02:04.712
Step 4: Change only the fork

00:02:04.712 --> 00:02:20.812
Step 5: Verify the original survives

00:02:20.812 --> 00:02:40.893
Step 6: Delete the fork

00:02:40.893 --> 00:02:51.306
A photo of the river

00:02:51.306 --> 00:03:01.626
Disk usage stays flat

00:03:01.626 --> 00:03:13.866
